{"tid":1726402,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[重推]全體和理非心聲: 係我哋做得吾夠, 感激前線所有","createTime":"2019-11-16T06:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T18:34:47.000Z","uid":252069,"like":179,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"d44cdb6899cd21e6bcc0f880c744561d4e63e5b8","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:49:35.000Z","msg":"我哋和理非明明同是爭取五大訴求<br />\n但係前線手足打生打死<br />\n我哋就將<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">抗爭外判</span></span></strong>, 淨係識匿喺屋企做鍵盤戰士, 最多落街屌黑警<br />\n有不反嘅遊行比黑警嚇兩嚇就<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">縮沙</span></span></strong><br />\n連罷工呢d咁無危險性嘅事我哋都做到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">唔湯唔水</span></strong></span><br />\n呢兩日好似有令黑警收一收手完全係手足<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">搵命博</span></span></strong>返來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講返今日七十歲過身嗰位伯伯, 係我哋嘅和理非嘅錯<br />\n雖然係人定鬼打定TK都未知, 但係有人死一定無人想<br />\n呢個係悲劇, 我好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然而出人命我唔會怪前線手足<br />\n因為就算係藍絲死都係我哋和理非出唔夠力, 導致<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍更藍黃更黃都係因為我</span></strong></span><br />\n仲滿口仁義道德話死咗人係前線太過份, 同為和理非我睇到覺得自己<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好醜</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自問無資格屌手足, 我自問<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廢到無得再廢</span></span></strong>, 但係我仲想幫手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">點幫手?</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n手足做得唔完美要改善一定有, 對某d人造成損害都有一定<br />\n然而任何人要怪罪搵人負責, 入我哋數!<br />\n要賠錢就由我哋出, 衰d講就算要坐監就由我哋去坐!<br />\n明明我哋都佔一樣大嘅責任, 我哋仲行得走得, 有手足<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">斷手斷腳失明冇命</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲屌手足我就唔敢再講自己有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">廉恥!</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日話好彩贏咗就話煲底除裝相見<br />\n我話你知就算加埋你好彩到冇一個前線手足要坐監<br />\n都只係得少部份前線手足可以無穿無爛仲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">行得走得</span></strong></span>出來同你見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有少少差池我真係無面目見你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔割</span></span></strong>唔係口號, 係覺得自己唔係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">苟且偷生</span></strong></span>嘅信念!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋自己睇<br />\n我成年後直到今年六月前加埋無喊過三次<br />\n但呢個係唯一一樣野令我諗親都眼紅鼻酸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i2Nw61z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi2Nw61z.jpg&h=7f6c14fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CzTbtTFM7Zw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCzTbtTFM7Zw&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=50374386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CzTbtTFM7Zw</a>"},{"pid":"64284f4d393fadd200d9cc92c34633e750ad06f4","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:50:10.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"ceefa2ba24897aba896469bc4a7caa6303670f8c","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:52:42.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"676eb6664425a85b6d90c9f19f70911ca12ec41b","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:54:53.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"4df3bf454301a1a5cc432ab274933f434e71c1d3","tid":1726402,"uid":259993,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"64284f4d393fadd200d9cc92c34633e750ad06f4","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:50:10.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:56:13.000Z","msg":"和理非好多嘢可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文宣一定要做 一為區選 二為勇武做盾 大家出去set路障可以整埋巨型時事牆俾燥底司機乘客睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e20527e9de6fb50aeee0ba824a05ddc25566d44","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:59:18.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"3e3a72f7e52627da5fd0a0a962ace20771d4cf7b","tid":1726402,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:03:26.000Z","msg":"［區選］藍絲散水運動，正式開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1726325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1726325</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"30546284713751e0bc7fa6403f4ac188da4e92d3","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:03:45.000Z","msg":"自推 5/10"},{"pid":"4a4b60ba65ff9b03c3b909778c965ef27a156050","tid":1726402,"uid":155012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:04:25.000Z","msg":"連登班冷氣佬推下post la"},{"pid":"3b566730b3245d8ac452870f5ce4e6334d4eb540","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:17:13.000Z","msg":"自推 6/10"},{"pid":"467975061efc2925441b1c73699234db7688d6f7","tid":1726402,"uid":120156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:18:09.000Z","msg":"認真post冇人推 分化post一大堆"},{"pid":"6e1d4e6aa7cbcbe7723e0dd64cd63249ca88fcb4","tid":1726402,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:18:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"31f905a79d3dc6bb25cdc10187f0a56d99dbfbb6","tid":1726402,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7668cabd0dde2a05982d83b49518566b20decf0c","tid":1726402,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2c9b9bb5fac410132052e6624ccc523bed9fe7","tid":1726402,"uid":299490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:30:51.000Z","msg":"1118-1122 黎明行動討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1726123\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1726123</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當我地難得搵到真正春袋，亦連續數日行之有效時，叫休息叫停個班，對唔對得住周同學，荃灣警署被強姦少女，葵涌被殺手足，西灣河被槍擊手足同過去半年犧牲嘅其他同路人？"},{"pid":"b11dba5ab0b9dbe20edd599b4ea933a56b57b689","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:37:02.000Z","msg":"自推 7/10"},{"pid":"1d6e3942ad54fbac44bc5a6e3103a32fe8eee425","tid":1726402,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:41:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd323ba06ef2c8082db72726c514ed02b3491ff6","tid":1726402,"uid":335348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:44:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726209/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726209/page/1</a><br />\n深度分析，大家可以都睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2882260334489913fcb52d5915c59e378da721","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:47:24.000Z","msg":"自推 8/10"},{"pid":"491dce78b88abc5ce52d4da887a7b6647baac6f8","tid":1726402,"uid":292091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:51:18.000Z","msg":"推呢個<br />\n出面一堆分化post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56bee13a6d89c86e92a6bfe2f78af390553862c","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:53:24.000Z","msg":"自推 9/10"},{"pid":"54add0072e5d0108015c19a8e337b323a1064a01","tid":1726402,"uid":139458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:54:02.000Z","msg":"不分化"},{"pid":"1a3bde888c5fd44bfcaf206acaeeb3be7a498be9","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:57:11.000Z","msg":"自推 10/10"},{"pid":"034ff27c4aa840aee5507fb060682c0ae698b3ea","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:00:40.000Z","msg":"以後有咩裝錯裝、c錯鳥、爆錯玻璃<br />\n無論係咪有證據甚至好確切證據懷疑係鬼做<br />\n全世界都吾好話<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">&quot;吾係手足做&quot;</span></span></strong><br />\n你應該話<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">&quot;係我做得不足, 我會努力!&quot;</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9936084e23c53ab0692ebe21f2dadf642f32b2fe","tid":1726402,"uid