 我會努力!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8f9ecc511f2402ef8c1d15b58459d72564a50ed5","tid":1726402,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feab11a3043d8f35c55f476c9c9a04a010db6194","tid":1726402,"uid":289115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d44cdb6899cd21e6bcc0f880c744561d4e63e5b8","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:49:35.000Z","msg":"我哋和理非明明同是爭取五大訴求<br />\n但係前線手足打生打死<br />\n我哋就將<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">抗爭外判</span></span></strong>, 淨係識匿喺屋企做鍵盤戰士, 最多落街屌黑警<br />\n有不反嘅遊行比黑警嚇兩嚇就<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">縮沙</span></span></strong><br />\n連罷工呢d咁無危險性嘅事我哋都做到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">唔湯唔水</span></strong></span><br />\n呢兩日好似有令黑警收一收手完全係手足<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">搵命博</span></span></strong>返來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講返今日七十歲過身嗰位伯伯, 係我哋嘅和理非嘅錯<br />\n雖然係人定鬼打定TK都未知, 但係有人死一定無人想<br />\n呢個係悲劇, 我好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然而出人命我唔會怪前線手足<br />\n因為就算係藍絲死都係我哋和理非出唔夠力, 導致<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍更藍黃更黃都係因為我</span></strong></span><br />\n仲滿口仁義道德話死咗人係前線太過份, 同為和理非我睇到覺得自己<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好醜</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自問無資格屌手足, 我自問<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廢到無得再廢</span></span></strong>, 但係我仲想幫手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">點幫手?</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n手足做得唔完美要改善一定有, 對某d人造成損害都有一定<br />\n然而任何人要怪罪搵人負責, 入我哋數!<br />\n要賠錢就由我哋出, 衰d講就算要坐監就由我哋去坐!<br />\n明明我哋都佔一樣大嘅責任, 我哋仲行得走得, 有手足<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">斷手斷腳失明冇命</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲屌手足我就唔敢再講自己有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">廉恥!</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日話好彩贏咗就話煲底除裝相見<br />\n我話你知就算加埋你好彩到冇一個前線手足要坐監<br />\n都只係得少部份前線手足可以無穿無爛仲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">行得走得</span></strong></span>出來同你見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有少少差池我真係無面目見你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔割</span></span></strong>唔係口號, 係覺得自己唔係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">苟且偷生</span></strong></span>嘅信念!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋自己睇<br />\n我成年後直到今年六月前加埋無喊過三次<br />\n但呢個係唯一一樣野令我諗親都眼紅鼻酸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i2Nw61z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi2Nw61z.jpg&h=7f6c14fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CzTbtTFM7Zw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCzTbtTFM7Zw&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=50374386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CzTbtTFM7Zw</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35714b56be5f3172c7500aaf27e12ad5b6b8bf86","tid":1726402,"uid":253952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37500b7032886694ddf6ab84c2c340070b081254","tid":1726402,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:30:30.000Z","msg":"講得好啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee87d6b67d4b5c65489ab7e3345464539daa376","tid":1726402,"uid":269119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64284f4d393fadd200d9cc92c34633e750ad06f4","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:50:10.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SzSQJO5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSzSQJO5.png&h=44a9c49c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8888fdf4018f093944a08d88d81b7dd1d170ada1","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:53:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b02880d0617a70427f78d077fd3e47390744546","tid":1726402,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:53:40.000Z","msg":"勇武加油"},{"pid":"7dbe32ee4acd2591b597d78b5b0ae9346169c4e0","tid":1726402,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:54:18.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"60f339b6aad2e1187aae847214ca25af4a8704a6","tid":1726402,"uid":335348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d44cdb6899cd21e6bcc0f880c744561d4e63e5b8","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:49:35.000Z","msg":"我哋和理非明明同是爭取五大訴求<br />\n但係前線手足打生打死<br />\n我哋就將<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">抗爭外判</span></span></strong>, 淨係識匿喺屋企做鍵盤戰士, 最多落街屌黑警<br />\n有不反嘅遊行比黑警嚇兩嚇就<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">縮沙</span></span></strong><br />\n連罷工呢d咁無危險性嘅事我哋都做到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">唔湯唔水</span></strong></span><br />\n呢兩日好似有令黑警收一收手完全係手足<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">搵命博</span></span></strong>返來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講返今日七十歲過身嗰位伯伯, 係我哋嘅和理非嘅錯<br />\n雖然係人定鬼打定TK都未知, 但係有人死一定無人想<br />\n呢個係悲劇, 我好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然而出人命我唔會怪前線手足<br />\n因為就算係藍絲死都係我哋和理非出唔夠力, 導致<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍更藍黃更黃都係因為我</span></strong></span><br />\n仲滿口仁義道德話死咗人係前線太過份, 同為和理非我睇到覺得自己<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好醜</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自問無資格屌手足, 我自問<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廢到無得再廢</span></span></strong>, 但係我仲想幫手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">點幫手?</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n手足做得唔完美要改善一定有, 對某d人造成損害都有一定<br />\n然而任何人要怪罪搵人負責, 入我哋數!<br />\n要賠錢就由我哋出, 衰d講就算要坐監就由我哋去坐!<br />\n明明我哋都佔一樣大嘅責任, 我哋仲行得走得, 有手足<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">斷手斷腳失明冇命</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲屌手足我就唔敢再講自己有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">廉恥!</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日話好彩贏咗就話煲底除裝相見<br />\n我話你知就算加埋你好彩到冇一個前線手足要坐監<br />\n都只係得少部份前線手足可以無穿無爛仲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">行得走得</span></strong></span>出來同你見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有少少差池我真係無面目見你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔割</span></span></strong>唔係口號, 係覺得自己唔係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">苟且偷生</span></strong></span>嘅信念!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋自己睇<br />\n我成年後直到今年六月前加埋無喊過三次<br />\n但呢個係唯一一樣野令我諗親都眼紅鼻酸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i2Nw61z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi2Nw61z.jpg&h=7f6c14fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CzTbtTFM7Zw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCzTbtTFM7Zw&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=50374386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CzTbtTFM7Zw</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:58:37.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726209/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726209/page/1</a><br />\n深度分析，大家可以都睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9738acabbda60fc38481cdd0f5fc194e79bb4de3","tid":1726402,"uid":70417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:58:42.000Z","msg":"睇完咁多字<br />\n都唔知你重點想講咩<br />\n淨係睇到和理非覺得勇武比人拉好慘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c82cd2b3bdae8598e6b2660eecd1547155fa24c","tid":1726402,"uid":336561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d283e23354027c72c91dda03e94703c4d08e41e","tid":1726402,"uid":336561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:21:46.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0bd17acbe8525daffe6397684e9091b83c4a3c","tid":1726402,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:40:21.000Z","msg":"自推啊!!!"},{"pid":"8a27cfee5132d851a3716d67f17cd6463eea146c","tid":1726402,"uid":119597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}